It’s FRIDAYYYY! And I’m gonna celebrate with what I call the 💜Purple Dragon💜 using @butterflycannontequila 😋 
This is really a white dragon, but because the Butterfly Cannon blue tequila is, well, BLUE thanks to the natural vegetable juice coloring - it comes out looking purple! Directions below ⬇️ 

2 oz Butterfly Cannon blue tequila 
0.75 oz Cointreau 
0.75 oz lemon juice
1 egg white

Add all ingredients to shaker tin. Shake vigorously WITHOUT ice for 30 seconds. Strain into chilled coupe glass (I don’t own a coupe glass so I had to improvise 🙃 will gladly take barware donations 🤗)

The perfect Mocktail for your Valentines Day celebration! (Inspired by @everyday_abby )

Strawberry champagne margarita 
Rim margarita glass with valentines sprinkles and fill with ice
Muddle 2-3 strawberries in shaker tin
Add ice
1.5 oz @nkdldy tequila alternative 
.75 oz alcohol free triple sec
SHAKE SHAKE SHAKE
Strain into glass 
Top with @frewines alcohol removed champagne
Use the back of a bar spoon to gently incorporate champagne into the margarita 
Sip and enjoy 💋

It’s official - I have found the perfect fall drink 😋 

Here’s how to make an apple cider old fashioned 🍎 
Muddle together 2 tsp brown sugar & 3-4 dashes of angostura bitters
Add ice, 2 oz of your favorite bourbon (I used Gentleman Jack), 1.5 oz apple cider and .5 oz fresh lemon juice
Stir baby stir
Strain over ice!
Garnish with apple slices and a cinnamon stick and ENJOY 😊
